    "We discuss the inference behaviour when each of these templates are used.",
    "For Script the model is expected to produce a well-structured SQL script.",
    "In this scenario, the structured data table provided in the prompt is temporarily loaded in memory using a lightweight database engine, and the script execution on the table produces the output.",
    "For Arithmetic the model is expected to predict a well formed arithmetic expression.",
    "This expression is evaluated by a calculator and the resulting value passed as output."
